timing_all_reg...lude_icg_cells(25.10)  timing_all_reg...lude_icg_cells(25.10)

Name
       timing_all_registers_include_icg_cells

Syntax
       timing_all_registers_include_icg_cells

       {true | false}

       Default: true

       Includes  integrated  clock  gating  (ICG)  cell  information  from the
       all_registers report output.

       When set to false, the global does not allow the  all_registers  report
       output to display ICG cell details.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

